01:10:05,880 --> 01:10:08,269
I'm getting the hell outta here!

942
01:10:09,840 --> 01:10:12,479
Too goddamn sultry in here!

943
01:10:16,840 --> 01:10:18,831
Where you goin'?

944
01:10:18,920 --> 01:10:21,309
I'm gonna kill the bitch.

945
01:10:21,880 --> 01:10:24,440
- You want anything?
- You can get me a Chunky.

946
01:10:32,560 --> 01:10:36,473
- Come here, Mrs Lift.
- You stay away from me, you murderer!

947
01:10:41,080 --> 01:10:42,513
Momma...

948
01:10:42,760 --> 01:10:44,159
Mrs Lift!

949
01:10:44,560 --> 01:10:46,596
- (Owen) Momma!
- Murderer! Murderer!

950
01:10:48,720 --> 01:10:51,029
Momma... Momma...

951
01:10:51,400 --> 01:10:55,598
Sultry? I'll show you
something sultry, Mrs Lift!

952
01:10:55,680 --> 01:10:57,238
G, 54.

953
01:10:57,720 --> 01:11:02,111
Stupid bingo! Don't you idiots know
there's a murderer loose on this train?!

954
01:11:02,760 --> 01:11:05,354
- Mrs Lift, come back here.
- Bingo bastards.

955
01:11:05,440 --> 01:11:07,351
My mother's a little overmedicated.

956
01:11:07,440 --> 01:11:11,353
Murderer! Murderer!
There's a murderer on the train.

957
01:11:11,720 --> 01:11:14,792
Wake up, you nutheads! Murderer!

958
01:11:15,120 --> 01:11:16,633
Excuse me. Excuse me.

959
01:11:16,720 --> 01:11:19,234
Wake up! There's a murderer on the train!

960
01:11:20,000 --> 01:11:21,479
Mrs Lift?

961
01:11:22,640 --> 01:11:24,631
Aarrghhh!

962
01:11:25,360 --> 01:11:28,750
- Mrs Lift, be careful!
- Get away from me, you murderer!

963
01:11:30,600 --> 01:11:32,511
- No!
- (Momma yells)

964
01:11:36,240 --> 01:11:39,198
- Mrs Lift...
- Let me go, you murderer!

965
01:11:39,600 --> 01:11:40,919
Owen!

966
01:11:41,000 --> 01:11:43,230
- Larry, you'll kill her!
- Save me!

967
01:11:43,320 --> 01:11:46,949
I'm not tryin' to kill her!
I'm tryin' to save her, you toad!

968
01:11:52,840 --> 01:11:54,478
Come on, Mrs Lift!

969
01:11:59,160 --> 01:12:01,993
Owen! Save me!

970
01:12:05,360 --> 01:12:08,238
Aarrghhh!

971
01:12:13,760 --> 01:12:16,957
Owen! Save me!

972
01:12:17,040 --> 01:12:18,996
Owen!

973
01:12:19,080 --> 01:12:23,278
- What are you doin' to my momma?!
- Making a wish! What do you think?!

974
01:12:24,720 --> 01:12:26,676
Help!

975
01:12:26,760 --> 01:12:28,432
Oh, no! Larry!

976
01:12:44,680 --> 01:12:46,671
Oh, you saved me, my Owen!

977
01:12:46,760 --> 01:12:50,514
- Mrs Lift, are you OK?
- Beat it, chump!

978
01:12:52,000 --> 01:12:53,718
- Larry!
- Aarghhh!

979
01:12:57,360 --> 01:12:59,351
Bye, Larry!

980
01:13:04,920 --> 01:13:08,071
To tell you the truth,
it was all a little bit embarrassing.

981
01:13:08,160 --> 01:13:11,789
My earring fell over the rail.
I bent over to retrieve it.

982
01:13:11,880 --> 01:13:14,155
The last thing I remember,
I was in the water.

983
01:13:14,560 --> 01:13:16,949
She fell off the boat. She fell off the boat.

984
01:13:17,040 --> 01:13:19,474
The little bastard never laid a hand on her.

985
01:13:19,560 --> 01:13:21,630
This wonderful Adonis of the deep...

986
01:13:21,720 --> 01:13:24,314
Oh, I love that. "Adonis of the deep".

987
01:13:24,400 --> 01:13:27,312
