Momma and our experiences together.

1044
01:18:08,920 --> 01:18:10,911
What's your book about?

1045
01:18:13,520 --> 01:18:16,876
You wrote a book called Momma
and Owen and Owen's Friend Larry?

1046
01:18:16,960 --> 01:18:18,951
Yeah.

1047
01:18:19,840 --> 01:18:23,549
- It's all about our...
- (both).. experiences together.

1048
01:18:25,680 --> 01:18:28,114
